%h2 All Tools
%p.tools_description
  I care about the tools I use. This is a list of the tools I have used in various projects.
  Larger words are tools I have used more frequently and smaller words refer to tools that I
  am still learning something about. If you click on one of the words, you will see a list of
  the projects I have used that tool for.
  
%ul.cloud
  - @tools.each do |tool|
    %li{:class => "cloud-#{@size[tool.projects.count]}"}=link_to tool